    {
        "content": "<p>Early return is really an imperative concept, but there is a functional equivalent. You use functions like <code>Result.try</code> or <code>Task.await</code> to build up a pipeline of operations, and exit on the first failure. The back-passing feature in Roc was created to make this pattern ergonomic.</p>",
